452
00:20:37,130 --> 00:20:38,060
It's okay.

453
00:20:38,080 --> 00:20:39,360
It was my fault.

454
00:20:39,620 --> 00:20:41,460
I wanted to tighten it,

455
00:20:41,840 --> 00:20:43,390
but I winded it too tight.

456
00:20:43,830 --> 00:20:45,600
And the water valve wasn't closed. So here we are.

457
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:48,390
Sorry, I messed up.

458
00:20:49,210 --> 00:20:50,890
My mom and I have never been

459
00:20:50,980 --> 00:20:52,580
