499
00:22:33,440 --> 00:22:34,770
That's not necessary.

500
00:22:34,800 --> 00:22:35,920
What job?

501
00:22:36,980 --> 00:22:37,780
Gaogui,

502
00:22:38,260 --> 00:22:40,580
